seoMeta.name: smartphones
seoMeta.title: Cell Phones: Shop the Best Smartphones Online | Verizon
seoMeta.metaDescription: Whether you're a mobile-tech expert, novice or somewhere in between, Verizon has a smartphone for you. Shop the latest smartphones at Verizon today.
seoMeta.footerSubHead1: Choose the best new phone for your lifestyle
seoMeta.footerSubHead2: Shop cell phones from top brands with Verizon

footerContentBlock1.text: Choosing the right cell phone for you and your loved ones isn't easy. With so many different options to choose from, including the latest Apple iPhone, new Samsung Galaxy phones, and Google smartphones, it's important to pick a device that has the right features for the right person. Thankfully at Verizon, we offer a wide variety of phones to our customers to ensure there's a device for everyone.

There are many different factors that go into choosing a new phone, so it's important to figure out what is the most important feature you would like to get out of your device. Do you want a cell phone with a larger screen size, a new phone with a high quality camera, or a device with a long battery life to help you stay connected throughout your busy day? Do you have other devices that run on certain operating systems that you want to connect your phone to? Knowing what features you care about most in a smartphone will help you better narrow down your options.

Once you have an idea of what features are most important to you in a new phone, then you can start looking into what fits best into your budget. Here at Verizon, we are always offering various cell phone deals to help you get the phone you want at a price you will love. Additionally, we offer options like certified pre-owned phones that may be a smart choice for the budget conscious shopper.

footerContentBlock2.text: If you're an Apple product owner, you know how convenient it can be to keep all your devices connected. That said, you may be looking for a new smartphone and opting to go with one of the latest iPhone models. Choosing an iPhone will allow you to connect your iPad, Apple Watch, and AirPods seamlessly to your new phone.

More interested in an Android device? Both Samsung phones and Google Pixels run on Android's operating system. A Samsung Galaxy phone will pair perfectly with a Galaxy Tab and Galaxy Watch, while a Google smartphone will connect to a Pixel Watch to get your phone's notifications right at your wrist.

No matter which smartphone you end up choosing, it's important that you keep your new phone protected with the right accessories. When it comes to your smartphone, bumps and drops are inevitable, which is why buying a sturdy phone case and screen protector when you buy your new phone is a smart investment. Here at Verizon, we carry a wide variety of phone accessories, so whether you're looking for a stylish or sturdy option, we have you covered.
